_sText: "fy_veranda3" This is a medium/large, symmetrical Fight Yard style map. There are three levels of play, and players can go on almost all the ledges except for the top ones. If you've played my other veranda maps then you will love this one! HFGL Buy zones are included. Please download, comment and enjoy! - 64 Spawns - 3d skybox - Cubemaps - Optimized for better FPS - Overview radar map - Buy Zones - Nav File for bots - Pakrated Blair (Bobpoblo) Burkhardt - Level Design http://www.fpsbanana.com/members/776402
